lead_paragraph: Four-times champion Sebastian Vettel feels the sudden departure of technical director James Allison will not have a major impact on his Ferrari team in the immediate future.

headline.print_headline: Losing Allison Won't Affect Ferrari Much in the Short-Term: Vettel
